5	 * the strength, giving a weighty, layered parallax. Movement is deliberate and
6	 * non-elastic (EASE.SETTLE only) — never bouncy. The rect is read once per
7	 * pointerenter; the per-move path allocates nothing (two pre-built quickTo
8	 * setters mutate the same two transforms).
